ExtAudioRecorder - Class in com.cs394.jas38.pdultrasonicclassification
---------------------------------------------------------------

CALL NAME : ExtAudioRecorder

FUNCTION : Records audio from the mic, and saves in a WAV format

AMENDMENTS : Created by http://i-liger.com/article/android-wav-audio-recording Found and used the class Denise had created.

ExtAudioRecorder(boolean, int, int, int, int) - Constructor for class com.cs394.jas38.pdultrasonicclassification.ExtAudioRecorder

ExtAudioRecorder.State - Enum in com.cs394.jas38.pdultrasonicclassification
